txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Dirty wings from the hendrevail and bats found in Ered Luin. Collect them and deliver them to Dorri at Gondamon to earn favour with Thorin's Hall.
'Hendrevail work with the Dourhands, vile creatures, and bats are nothing more than flying vermin.\n\n'Your efforts will echo through the halls.'
'Best get moving...the hendrevail and bats out there are not going to come to you, you know.'
Dorri wants dirty wings. Dorri can be found standing at the west gate of Gondamon.
Deliver the dirty wings to Dorri at Gondamon
You have accepted a task to acquire dirty wings. You are to deliver them to Dorri at the western gate of Gondamon to earn favour with Thorin's Hall.
Wanted: Dirty wings from the hendrevail and bats found in Ered Luin.
